WEBVTT

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:16.700 line:80%
[Baxia Manor]

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:20.600 line:80%
Don't hurt my mother...

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:22.760 line:80%
Don't hurt my mother...

00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:26.510 line:80%
Don't hurt my mother...

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:28.670 line:80%
Don't...

00:00:30.190 --> 00:00:30.870 line:80%
Don't...

00:00:30.870 --> 00:00:32.000 line:80%
Give me the food box.

00:00:32.510 --> 00:00:33.000 line:80%
Yes.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:34.260 line:80%
Wait for me at the door.

00:00:34.440 --> 00:00:35.080 line:80%
Yes.

00:00:35.590 --> 00:00:36.590 line:80%
Don't...

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:38.120 line:80%
hurt...

00:00:38.910 --> 00:00:39.950 line:80%
my mother...

00:00:43.080 --> 00:00:45.210 line:80%
Don't be afraid, Little Young Master.

00:00:45.550 --> 00:00:47.510 line:80%
I brought you something to eat.

00:00:49.120 --> 00:00:49.910 line:80%
Hurt...

00:00:49.910 --> 00:00:51.470 line:80%
Your mother is fine.

00:00:52.150 --> 00:00:53.120 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:00:53.800 --> 00:00:54.870 line:80%
Eat up.

00:00:55.510 --> 00:00:58.440 line:80%
Don't hurt my mother...

00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:01.720 line:80%
Hurt my mother...

00:01:02.760 --> 00:01:03.720 line:80%
Don't...

00:01:03.720 --> 00:01:04.920 line:80%
Little Young Master,

00:01:05.110 --> 00:01:06.590 line:80%
You haven't eaten or drunk

00:01:06.590 --> 00:01:08.080 line:80%
much for days.

00:01:08.589 --> 00:01:09.750 line:80%
If this keeps up,

00:01:09.870 --> 00:01:12.310 line:80%
your health will suffer.

00:01:12.390 --> 00:01:15.510 line:80%
Don't hurt my mother...

00:01:18.560 --> 00:01:19.560 line:80%
Don't...

00:01:19.720 --> 00:01:21.030 line:80%
Little Young Master,

00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:23.030 line:80%
if you don't eat,

00:01:23.390 --> 00:01:26.390 line:80%
how will you have the strength
to protect your mother?

00:01:41.150 --> 00:01:43.279 line:80%
Slow down! There is more.

00:01:57.080 --> 00:01:58.510 line:80%
My Little Young Master!

00:01:59.150 --> 00:02:00.560 line:80%
You mustn't do this!

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:01.480 line:80%
You mustn't do this!

00:02:01.480 --> 00:02:02.670 line:80%
That's ink!

00:02:02.670 --> 00:02:04.530 line:80%
You can't eat it! You can't eat it!

00:02:05.110 --> 00:02:06.590 line:80%
Don't eat it. Don't eat it.

00:02:07.440 --> 00:02:09.480 line:80%
What should I do now?

00:02:15.390 --> 00:02:16.600 line:80%
The killing of a maid

00:02:16.950 --> 00:02:18.280 line:80%
made him sick with fear?

00:02:19.510 --> 00:02:21.040 line:80%
Have you forgotten, Nanny?

00:02:21.710 --> 00:02:23.110 line:80%
When I was his age,

00:02:23.510 --> 00:02:25.800 line:80%
I survived the fire in the Eastern Palace.

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:29.480 line:80%
The Little Young Master
grew up without you around,

00:02:29.710 --> 00:02:32.230 line:80%
so he didn't inherit your courage.

00:02:32.600 --> 00:02:34.360 line:80%
Even the slightest trouble

00:02:34.360 --> 00:02:36.600 line:80%
is enough to fill him with fear.

00:02:37.110 --> 00:02:40.390 line:80%
I fear that if this goes on,

00:02:40.390 --> 00:02:42.670 line:80%
something bad might happen to him.

00:02:45.480 --> 00:02:46.430 line:80%
So?

00:02:47.600 --> 00:02:50.480 line:80%
So, with all respect,

00:02:50.480 --> 00:02:52.950 line:80%
I want to find a playmate
for the Little Young Master,

00:02:52.950 --> 00:02:57.110 line:80%
hoping it might improve his condition.

00:02:58.950 --> 00:02:59.830 line:80%
Who do you want?

00:03:01.390 --> 00:03:03.430 line:80%
I heard from Xun that

00:03:04.110 --> 00:03:07.480 line:80%
Her Ladyship was close to the Fan family
in Lin'an Town.

00:03:07.480 --> 00:03:08.670 line:80%
They had a deep bond.

00:03:09.160 --> 00:03:12.430 line:80%
The Fan family's youngest daughter
happens to be here.

00:03:12.430 --> 00:03:13.360 line:80%
Perhaps...

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:23.490 line:80%
Since you've already decided,

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:25.400 line:80%
just go ask Yuanqing for her.

00:03:26.430 --> 00:03:27.200 line:80%
Yes.

00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:14.080 line:80%
Don't be afraid, little girl.

00:04:14.880 --> 00:04:16.670 line:80%
I'm taking you to meet someone.

00:04:38.750 --> 00:04:39.990 line:80%
Little Young Master,

00:04:40.550 --> 00:04:42.550 line:80%
please pause and take a rest.

00:04:44.360 --> 00:04:47.280 line:80%
Little Young Master,
look who I brought here.

00:04:53.670 --> 00:04:55.040 line:80%
Yu Bao'er.

00:05:30.160 --> 00:05:31.310 line:80%
Yu Bao'er.

00:05:39.750 --> 00:05:40.360 line:80%
Here.

00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:55.430 line:80%
Alright, Bao'er.

00:05:55.430 --> 00:05:57.160 line:80%
I know you want to cry.

00:05:57.160 --> 00:05:58.920 line:80%
Don't cry.

00:06:00.960 --> 00:06:03.110 line:80%
I'm here to protect you.

00:06:05.280 --> 00:06:06.540 line:80%
It's alright, Bao'er.

00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:08.990 line:80%
I will protect you.

00:06:13.230 --> 00:06:14.400 line:80%
This is for you.

00:06:14.990 --> 00:06:17.310 line:80%
If you are ever in danger,

00:06:17.310 --> 00:06:18.310 line:80%
just blow on this,

00:06:18.840 --> 00:06:20.900 line:80%
and someone will come to protect you.

00:06:21.990 --> 00:06:23.840 line:80%
R-Really?

00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:26.160 line:80%
Really.

00:06:29.550 --> 00:06:31.840 line:80%
Once, I fell into a well,

00:06:31.840 --> 00:06:33.670 line:80%
and I screamed until I was hoarse.

00:06:33.670 --> 00:06:35.280 line:80%
When Father found me,

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:36.870 line:80%
I couldn't even speak.

00:06:37.400 --> 00:06:40.160 line:80%
So Father made me this bamboo whistle.

00:06:40.160 --> 00:06:41.480 line:80%
If you blow it,

00:06:41.480 --> 00:06:43.400 line:80%
someone will come to protect you.

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:45.040 line:80%
It really works.

00:06:45.990 --> 00:06:48.040 line:80%
Le-Let me tell you.

00:06:48.230 --> 00:06:49.360 line:80%
These past few days...

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:50.360 line:80%
And then...

00:06:50.360 --> 00:06:51.310 line:80%
he took...

00:06:51.310 --> 00:06:53.160 line:80%
a stick this big

00:06:53.520 --> 00:06:55.070 line:80%
and hit her with it.

00:06:55.070 --> 00:06:57.520 line:80%
She was bleeding.

00:06:57.630 --> 00:06:59.360 line:80%
I didn't even dare to look at it.

00:08:25.370 --> 00:08:30.740 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:08:30.840 --> 00:08:33.380 line:80%
[Episode 21]

00:08:39.709 --> 00:08:41.170 line:80%
Everyone, gather around!

00:08:44.520 --> 00:08:45.580 line:80%
Come out! Come out!

00:08:45.880 --> 00:08:46.590 line:80%
Gather around!

00:08:46.590 --> 00:08:47.280 line:80%
Come out!

00:08:48.400 --> 00:08:49.920 line:80%
Come out! Get up!

00:08:50.350 --> 00:08:51.350 line:80%
-Get up.
-Let's go.

00:08:51.350 --> 00:08:52.710 line:80%
Gather around!

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:54.400 line:80%
Get up and gather around!

00:08:55.040 --> 00:08:55.570 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:08:56.040 --> 00:08:58.240 line:80%
-Gather around.
-Take one each.

00:08:58.240 --> 00:08:59.900 line:80%
-Let's go.
-Come out and work.

00:08:59.950 --> 00:09:00.880 line:80%
Grab your tools.

00:09:01.240 --> 00:09:02.000 line:80%
Go now!

00:09:02.520 --> 00:09:03.670 line:80%
Everyone take one.

00:09:03.800 --> 00:09:04.520 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:09:05.640 --> 00:09:09.100 line:80%
Come out quickly. It's time
to quarry rocks and build the road.

00:09:09.190 --> 00:09:09.880 line:80%
Young lady.

00:09:10.550 --> 00:09:11.750 line:80%
Gather around first!

00:09:12.040 --> 00:09:13.000 line:80%
Hurry up.

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:14.860 line:80%
Until your identity is verified,

00:09:14.880 --> 00:09:16.470 line:80%
you may not leave without permission.

00:09:16.470 --> 00:09:17.800 line:80%
Since you are a law-abiding citizen,

00:09:17.800 --> 00:09:19.200 line:80%
you should obey the laws.

00:09:20.310 --> 00:09:22.830 line:80%
I have had someone
deliver a letter to Jizhou.

00:09:22.830 --> 00:09:25.670 line:80%
You can leave
only after your identity is verified.

00:09:25.670 --> 00:09:26.710 line:80%
In the meantime,

00:09:26.880 --> 00:09:29.590 line:80%
go quarry some rocks
and build the road to earn your keep.

00:09:29.590 --> 00:09:30.430 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:09:31.350 --> 00:09:32.210 line:80%
Gather around!

00:09:34.120 --> 00:09:35.520 line:80%
-Hurry up.
-Come here.

00:09:35.950 --> 00:09:37.080 line:80%
Hurry up. Get up now.

00:09:37.830 --> 00:09:38.950 line:80%
Here. Get to work.

00:09:39.240 --> 00:09:39.950 line:80%
Go now.

00:09:42.670 --> 00:09:43.470 line:80%
Go now.

00:09:43.830 --> 00:09:44.830 line:80%
Come out, you all.

00:09:44.830 --> 00:09:45.670 line:80%
Give it to me.

00:09:45.670 --> 00:09:46.670 line:80%
Come on.

00:09:47.400 --> 00:09:48.800 line:80%
Stop sleeping. Hurry up.

00:09:50.240 --> 00:09:51.350 line:80%
One for each.

00:09:51.350 --> 00:09:52.120 line:80%
Hurry up.

00:09:54.470 --> 00:09:55.470 line:80%
Come out, you all.

00:09:55.640 --> 00:09:56.500 line:80%
Gather around!

00:09:58.190 --> 00:09:59.450 line:80%
Do you have your tools?

00:10:00.190 --> 00:10:01.470 line:80%
Listen up, everyone.

00:10:02.120 --> 00:10:03.310 line:80%
Pair up

00:10:03.670 --> 00:10:06.070 line:80%
and go to the back mountain
to dig for stones.

00:10:06.070 --> 00:10:08.470 line:80%
Men need to fill 10 large baskets.

00:10:09.070 --> 00:10:11.550 line:80%
Women need to fill 15 small baskets.

00:10:11.920 --> 00:10:13.450 line:80%
That will earn you one meal.

00:10:14.470 --> 00:10:16.550 line:80%
Stonemason Zhang, let's be partners today.

00:10:16.550 --> 00:10:18.410 line:80%
Mrs. Li, let's be partners today.

00:10:18.470 --> 00:10:19.240 line:80%
Sure.

00:10:20.130 --> 00:10:20.950 line:80%
This new girl

00:10:20.950 --> 00:10:22.400 line:80%
is so skinny.

00:10:22.400 --> 00:10:23.710 line:80%
She obviously can't work.

00:10:23.710 --> 00:10:25.160 line:80%
We can't partner with her.

00:10:25.160 --> 00:10:26.890 line:80%
Find someone young and strong.

00:10:27.830 --> 00:10:28.310 line:80%
Sir,

00:10:28.310 --> 00:10:29.240 line:80%
let's partner up.

00:10:29.240 --> 00:10:30.970 line:80%
Follow me and you'll have food.

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:32.250 line:80%
Let's pair up.

00:10:32.520 --> 00:10:33.650 line:80%
Let's pair up later.

00:10:35.880 --> 00:10:37.680 line:80%
If you partner with this old man,

00:10:38.240 --> 00:10:40.040 line:80%
we can go easy on you.

00:10:40.470 --> 00:10:42.130 line:80%
10 small baskets will be fine.

00:10:43.040 --> 00:10:44.040 line:80%
That's a bargain.

00:10:45.800 --> 00:10:47.200 line:80%
Let me carry that for you.

00:10:47.670 --> 00:10:49.350 line:80%
Even though I'm old,

00:10:49.350 --> 00:10:50.430 line:80%
I still have my pride.

00:10:50.430 --> 00:10:53.640 line:80%
How could I let a woman help me?

00:10:53.920 --> 00:10:56.280 line:80%
I can dig 10 baskets by myself.

00:10:59.800 --> 00:11:00.590 line:80%
Young lady,

00:11:01.190 --> 00:11:02.350 line:80%
that Old Tao

00:11:02.350 --> 00:11:03.430 line:80%
is very weird.

00:11:03.590 --> 00:11:05.880 line:80%
He talks pedantically all day long.

00:11:05.880 --> 00:11:07.190 line:80%
No one understands him.

00:11:07.190 --> 00:11:08.120 line:80%
Just ignore him.

00:11:11.310 --> 00:11:12.280 line:80%
Set off!

00:11:13.920 --> 00:11:14.640 line:80%
Move!

00:11:16.950 --> 00:11:18.310 line:80%
Sir, let me help you.

00:11:19.880 --> 00:11:21.160 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:11:21.830 --> 00:11:23.400 line:80%
This new girl is nice.

00:11:25.640 --> 00:11:27.370 line:80%
Then I'll carry the hoe for you.

00:11:28.240 --> 00:11:28.800 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:11:28.800 --> 00:11:30.670 line:80%
Go now! Time to work!

00:11:30.670 --> 00:11:32.190 line:80%
Time to work! Go!

00:11:40.830 --> 00:11:42.040 line:80%
Alright, this basket is full.

00:11:42.040 --> 00:11:42.920 line:80%
Help me lift it.

00:11:42.920 --> 00:11:43.520 line:80%
Here.

00:11:44.800 --> 00:11:45.710 line:80%
Be careful.

00:11:55.470 --> 00:11:56.520 line:80%
Be careful!

00:11:58.950 --> 00:11:59.760 line:80%
Sir.

00:12:00.430 --> 00:12:01.690 line:80%
Judging by your speed,

00:12:02.230 --> 00:12:04.290 line:80%
you haven't eaten for days, have you?

00:12:04.310 --> 00:12:05.170 line:80%
Let me help you.

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:07.240 line:80%
I can do it myself!

00:12:07.240 --> 00:12:08.240 line:80%
Get out of the way!

00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:10.760 line:80%
Come here!

00:12:12.710 --> 00:12:13.970 line:80%
Everyone, be careful!

00:12:14.160 --> 00:12:15.120 line:80%
Young lady,

00:12:15.400 --> 00:12:16.800 line:80%
how are you so strong?

00:12:19.590 --> 00:12:21.880 line:80%
You sound like a scholar.

00:12:22.310 --> 00:12:24.120 line:80%
Why are you moving rocks here?

00:12:24.190 --> 00:12:26.350 line:80%
I was looking for my disciple
at the border.

00:12:26.350 --> 00:12:28.430 line:80%
Unexpectedly, I was caught
in a heavy rainstorm overnight

00:12:28.430 --> 00:12:29.760 line:80%
and couldn't continue my journey.

00:12:29.760 --> 00:12:31.690 line:80%
Then I was caught here by soldiers.

00:12:31.760 --> 00:12:34.360 line:80%
It must have been Wei Yigui
who blocked the way.

00:12:34.640 --> 00:12:36.520 line:80%
That fatherless bastard!

00:12:37.670 --> 00:12:38.800 line:80%
Who is Wei Yigui?

00:12:39.240 --> 00:12:41.070 line:80%
The Prime Minister, Wei Yan!

00:12:47.070 --> 00:12:48.070 line:80%
Stop watching.

00:12:48.070 --> 00:12:48.730 line:80%
Get to work!

00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:50.550 line:80%
Can I ask you another question?

00:12:50.550 --> 00:12:51.240 line:80%
Go ahead.

00:12:52.550 --> 00:12:54.680 line:80%
What does "fatherless bastard" mean?

00:12:56.310 --> 00:12:57.970 line:80%
You never went to school, huh?

00:12:58.400 --> 00:12:59.470 line:80%
Just a little.

00:12:59.640 --> 00:13:00.430 line:80%
Not much.

00:13:01.190 --> 00:13:03.040 line:80%
Then why should I teach you?

00:13:03.710 --> 00:13:04.590 line:80%
Forget it then.

00:13:23.550 --> 00:13:23.950 line:80%
You...

00:13:25.550 --> 00:13:27.280 line:80%
Nothing can be accomplished without rules.

00:13:27.280 --> 00:13:28.070 line:80%
Get in line!

00:13:29.240 --> 00:13:30.520 line:80%
Old man, don't get in the way.

00:13:30.520 --> 00:13:31.800 line:80%
We need to eat

00:13:31.800 --> 00:13:33.160 line:80%
so we can work.

00:13:33.590 --> 00:13:34.430 line:80%
You're so old.

00:13:34.550 --> 00:13:35.880 line:80%
You have no strength to work.

00:13:35.880 --> 00:13:36.800 line:80%
Go home and rest.

00:13:36.800 --> 00:13:37.310 line:80%
You...

00:13:37.640 --> 00:13:38.880 line:80%
You rude brat!

00:13:39.120 --> 00:13:41.160 line:80%
You utterly deranged canine!

00:13:41.280 --> 00:13:41.950 line:80%
Deranged?

00:13:42.400 --> 00:13:43.310 line:80%
You dared call me a dog?

00:13:43.310 --> 00:13:45.370 line:80%
So you do understand human language?

00:13:45.470 --> 00:13:47.070 line:80%
Bravo!

00:13:47.470 --> 00:13:48.710 line:80%
-Well done!
-Well done!

00:13:48.710 --> 00:13:50.190 line:80%
This girl is strong.

00:13:52.470 --> 00:13:53.400 line:80%
He deserves it.

00:13:53.400 --> 00:13:54.520 line:80%
You little girl.

00:13:54.520 --> 00:13:55.520 line:80%
You want to fight?

00:13:56.280 --> 00:13:57.610 line:80%
Who's causing trouble?

00:13:57.710 --> 00:13:58.840 line:80%
He is. He cut in line.

00:13:59.350 --> 00:14:00.410 line:80%
Sun Zhuangzhuang?

00:14:00.590 --> 00:14:01.640 line:80%
You are such a giant.

00:14:01.640 --> 00:14:02.830 line:80%
Why are you cutting in line?

00:14:02.830 --> 00:14:03.690 line:80%
Get to the back!

00:14:05.640 --> 00:14:06.240 line:80%
Well done.

00:14:06.310 --> 00:14:07.070 line:80%
Move!

00:14:08.640 --> 00:14:09.700 line:80%
Everyone, line up.

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:14.520 line:80%
Here.

00:14:24.640 --> 00:14:26.040 line:80%
Why are you looking at me?

00:14:26.310 --> 00:14:27.640 line:80%
Is there a bun on my face?

00:14:37.670 --> 00:14:39.000 line:80%
You are a learned man.

00:14:39.640 --> 00:14:41.640 line:80%
Why are you doing this rough work?

00:14:42.350 --> 00:14:44.760 line:80%
Don't you feel it's unfair
to eat coarse food?

00:14:44.760 --> 00:14:47.690 line:80%
You're the only one in the whole camp
with some taste.

00:14:48.310 --> 00:14:49.670 line:80%
When I just arrived in Jizhou,

00:14:49.670 --> 00:14:52.710 line:80%
I heard that brat disappeared again.

00:14:53.280 --> 00:14:55.670 line:80%
I wanted to go to Chongzhou to find him.

00:14:56.640 --> 00:14:57.700 line:80%
But I didn't expect

00:14:57.800 --> 00:14:59.130 line:80%
to leave the tiger's den

00:14:59.950 --> 00:15:02.240 line:80%
only to enter the wolf's lair.

00:15:03.070 --> 00:15:04.160 line:80%
Who's that brat?

00:15:04.350 --> 00:15:05.160 line:80%
Your son?

00:15:05.670 --> 00:15:07.240 line:80%
Half a son, I suppose.

00:15:08.350 --> 00:15:09.350 line:80%
Your son-in-law.

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:13.310 line:80%
You uneducated

00:15:13.830 --> 00:15:16.000 line:80%
and ignorant young girl.

00:15:16.310 --> 00:15:17.710 line:80%
It's my disciple.

00:15:24.470 --> 00:15:25.800 line:80%
My former husband

00:15:26.550 --> 00:15:27.950 line:80%
was also half a scholar.

00:15:28.880 --> 00:15:31.190 line:80%
It's a pity he hadn't taught me to read

00:15:31.670 --> 00:15:32.530 line:80%
before he left.

00:15:33.880 --> 00:15:36.610 line:80%
It's a pity that you're a widow
at such a young age.

00:15:36.950 --> 00:15:38.120 line:80%
My condolences.

00:15:38.240 --> 00:15:39.170 line:80%
My condolences.

00:15:39.710 --> 00:15:40.920 line:80%
I'm not a widow.

00:15:41.400 --> 00:15:42.930 line:80%
He went to the battlefield.

00:15:42.950 --> 00:15:44.240 line:80%
His martial arts are excellent.

00:15:44.240 --> 00:15:47.190 line:80%
You made it sound like he was dead.

00:15:54.350 --> 00:15:55.550 line:80%
I guess he's not dead.

00:16:00.040 --> 00:16:01.500 line:80%
It's cold in early spring.

00:16:01.880 --> 00:16:03.310 line:80%
Be careful not to catch a cold.

00:16:03.310 --> 00:16:04.040 line:80%
Put this on.

00:16:04.240 --> 00:16:04.800 line:80%
No need.

00:16:12.280 --> 00:16:14.830 line:80%
I've been stuck in this hellhole
for 2 months without a woman.

00:16:14.830 --> 00:16:15.920 line:80%
It's the first time I've seen

00:16:15.920 --> 00:16:17.550 line:80%
such a pretty young lady.

00:16:19.070 --> 00:16:20.710 line:80%
Don't pair up with this old geezer.

00:16:20.710 --> 00:16:21.670 line:80%
Team up with us.

00:16:21.800 --> 00:16:24.520 line:80%
We guarantee you'll eat and drink well.

00:16:25.160 --> 00:16:25.550 line:80%
Yeah.

00:16:25.550 --> 00:16:26.640 line:80%
Nonsense!

00:16:27.280 --> 00:16:28.810 line:80%
You lecherous scoundrels!

00:16:29.310 --> 00:16:30.800 line:80%
Although I am old,

00:16:31.070 --> 00:16:33.550 line:80%
I won't allow you to be so impudent!

00:16:33.550 --> 00:16:34.590 line:80%
Don't you dare come close!

00:16:34.590 --> 00:16:35.950 line:80%
Get lost!

00:16:35.950 --> 00:16:38.010 line:80%
Get out of the way! Stop making a fuss!

00:16:38.240 --> 00:16:39.640 line:80%
Raising a stick at me?

00:16:39.760 --> 00:16:41.090 line:80%
I've seen many rascals,

00:16:41.590 --> 00:16:43.760 line:80%
but never ones
who bully an old man like you guys.

00:16:43.760 --> 00:16:44.830 line:80%
Shameless.

00:16:45.640 --> 00:16:47.170 line:80%
There are no soldiers here.

00:16:47.310 --> 00:16:49.120 line:80%
I'll cripple this old man.
Do you believe me?

00:16:49.120 --> 00:16:49.880 line:80%
Try me!

00:16:50.000 --> 00:16:50.880 line:80%
Try you?

00:16:51.070 --> 00:16:52.870 line:80%
-See if I dare!
-I look prettier!

00:17:05.350 --> 00:17:06.280 line:80%
Jin.

00:17:06.310 --> 00:17:08.389 line:80%
It's first come, first served.

00:17:08.680 --> 00:17:10.280 line:80%
I spotted her first.

00:17:10.629 --> 00:17:12.000 line:80%
Don't fight me for her.

00:17:13.440 --> 00:17:15.310 line:80%
Don't be ungrateful.

00:17:15.869 --> 00:17:17.470 line:80%
I am trying to save your life.

00:17:17.590 --> 00:17:18.760 line:80%
I don't want to collect your corpse.

00:17:18.760 --> 00:17:19.820 line:80%
Do you understand?

00:17:20.110 --> 00:17:21.350 line:80%
Right, Mrs. Fan?

00:17:22.590 --> 00:17:24.350 line:80%
Mr. Jin!

00:17:24.590 --> 00:17:26.000 line:80%
Wait, you...

00:17:27.440 --> 00:17:28.760 line:80%
You dare bully Mrs. Fan?

00:17:28.760 --> 00:17:29.390 line:80%
Beat him!

00:17:29.390 --> 00:17:30.070 line:80%
Beat him!

00:17:30.070 --> 00:17:30.870 line:80%
Beat him!

00:17:31.440 --> 00:17:31.870 line:80%
Beat!

00:17:32.480 --> 00:17:33.210 line:80%
Don't fight!

00:17:34.150 --> 00:17:35.720 line:80%
Who's making trouble there?

00:17:35.720 --> 00:17:36.980 line:80%
You guys, come with me!

00:17:37.150 --> 00:17:38.720 line:80%
Take them all to the front lines.

00:17:38.720 --> 00:17:39.480 line:80%
Stop crying! Move!

00:17:39.480 --> 00:17:41.000 line:80%
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

00:17:41.870 --> 00:17:43.310 line:80%
Don't run!

00:17:43.630 --> 00:17:44.870 line:80%
You forgot...

00:17:44.870 --> 00:17:46.070 line:80%
We forgot the old man!

00:17:47.520 --> 00:17:48.180 line:80%
Be careful.

00:17:48.310 --> 00:17:48.630 line:80%
Don't run!

00:17:48.630 --> 00:17:49.960 line:80%
Don't shake my old bones

00:17:49.960 --> 00:17:51.440 line:80%
to pieces.

00:17:51.680 --> 00:17:52.310 line:80%
Hurry!

00:18:08.680 --> 00:18:10.960 line:80%
We'll come find you tonight.

00:18:11.280 --> 00:18:12.740 line:80%
Listen for the cat's meow.

00:18:47.730 --> 00:18:49.630 line:80%
[Women's Quarters No. 3]

00:19:14.800 --> 00:19:16.000 line:80%
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

00:19:20.910 --> 00:19:22.520 line:80%
It's about to rain. Where are we going?

00:19:22.520 --> 00:19:23.830 line:80%
It's fine. Follow me.

00:19:30.720 --> 00:19:31.520 line:80%
Someone's coming!

00:19:31.520 --> 00:19:33.040 line:80%
The fire! The fire!

00:19:52.070 --> 00:19:52.960 line:80%
Alright.

00:19:52.960 --> 00:19:53.910 line:80%
They've gone.

00:19:53.910 --> 00:19:54.570 line:80%
Light it up.

00:19:58.630 --> 00:19:59.630 line:80%
How is this place?

00:20:00.070 --> 00:20:02.240 line:80%
We'll meet here to talk from now on.

00:20:05.480 --> 00:20:06.800 line:80%
There's a reason for your success,

00:20:06.800 --> 00:20:07.630 line:80%
bro.

00:20:12.680 --> 00:20:14.350 line:80%
What is this good stuff?

00:20:14.480 --> 00:20:15.680 line:80%
There's so much of it.

00:20:19.070 --> 00:20:19.680 line:80%
Isn't...

00:20:21.630 --> 00:20:22.830 line:80%
Isn't this my mother's?

00:20:22.830 --> 00:20:23.480 line:80%
What?

00:20:23.590 --> 00:20:24.590 line:80%
Why is it here?

00:20:40.440 --> 00:20:41.590 line:80%
This is my sister's.

00:20:42.240 --> 00:20:43.280 line:80%
This is...

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:45.600 line:80%
the birthday gift I gave her.

00:20:45.630 --> 00:20:47.160 line:80%
She treasures it very much.

00:20:47.280 --> 00:20:48.940 line:80%
She carries it with her all day

00:20:50.350 --> 00:20:51.800 line:80%
and uses it all the time.

00:20:56.200 --> 00:20:57.310 line:80%
Why is it here?

00:20:59.000 --> 00:20:59.720 line:80%
Yeah.

00:21:09.550 --> 00:21:10.240 line:80%
Changyu.

00:21:10.480 --> 00:21:12.140 line:80%
A great calamity occurred...

00:21:13.800 --> 00:21:15.860 line:80%
And Lin'an was massacred by bandits.

00:21:18.070 --> 00:21:19.200 line:80%
Constable Wang,

00:21:20.520 --> 00:21:22.250 line:80%
Mrs. Yin from the noodle stall,

00:21:22.830 --> 00:21:24.070 line:80%
Chef Li,

00:21:25.240 --> 00:21:27.100 line:80%
the staff at Yixiang Restaurant,

00:21:27.910 --> 00:21:29.040 line:80%
Granny Kang,

00:21:30.350 --> 00:21:32.080 line:80%
and the neighbors in Xigu Lane—

00:21:33.000 --> 00:21:34.600 line:80%
half the people of Lin'an...

00:21:34.960 --> 00:21:36.070 line:80%
are dead.

00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:41.310 line:80%
What about my sister?

00:21:42.680 --> 00:21:43.830 line:80%
She's fine.

00:21:44.390 --> 00:21:46.440 line:80%
She hurt her leg while escaping.

00:21:47.040 --> 00:21:48.440 line:80%
She's bedridden for now.

00:21:48.760 --> 00:21:51.090 line:80%
The doctor said she'll lose her right leg.

00:21:52.110 --> 00:21:53.440 line:80%
She asked me to tell you

00:21:54.280 --> 00:21:56.210 line:80%
that she's waiting for you at home,

00:21:56.240 --> 00:21:57.840 line:80%
hoping for your safe return.

00:21:59.760 --> 00:22:00.690 line:80%
Well... Then...

00:22:01.440 --> 00:22:03.070 line:80%
Wh-What about my mother?

00:22:03.070 --> 00:22:04.480 line:80%
Is she...

00:22:08.310 --> 00:22:10.440 line:80%
Tell me. What happened to my mother?

00:22:11.310 --> 00:22:12.280 line:80%
Your mother...

00:22:15.070 --> 00:22:16.550 line:80%
She was paralyzed with fear

00:22:16.550 --> 00:22:17.870 line:80%
and didn't make it.

00:22:23.000 --> 00:22:25.330 line:80%
Before she passed,
she asked me to tell you

00:22:26.960 --> 00:22:28.820 line:80%
that no matter how hard life gets,

00:22:29.590 --> 00:22:31.070 line:80%
you must live on.

00:22:36.480 --> 00:22:37.150 line:80%
Mother!

00:22:39.830 --> 00:22:40.490 line:80%
Brother...

00:22:50.870 --> 00:22:52.130 line:80%
What about my grandma?

00:22:54.870 --> 00:22:56.400 line:80%
Grandma Jin is still alive.

00:22:56.910 --> 00:22:58.040 line:80%
But...

00:22:58.630 --> 00:22:59.910 line:80%
while escaping,

00:23:00.310 --> 00:23:01.440 line:80%
she hit her head.

00:23:04.760 --> 00:23:06.420 line:80%
She doesn't remember anyone.

00:23:13.870 --> 00:23:15.390 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao is still alive.

00:23:16.680 --> 00:23:19.070 line:80%
I... got separated from Changning.

00:23:20.070 --> 00:23:21.670 line:80%
I looked for her for 2 months,

00:23:23.200 --> 00:23:24.720 line:80%
but I couldn't find her.

00:23:28.350 --> 00:23:29.590 line:80%
Who did this?

00:23:30.070 --> 00:23:32.070 line:80%
Bandits from Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:23:33.390 --> 00:23:35.350 line:80%
I killed their Second Master.

00:23:36.440 --> 00:23:39.700 line:80%
But the mastermind behind the scene
is likely still alive.

00:23:40.680 --> 00:23:43.720 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing,
the heir apparent of Lord Changxin.

00:23:45.680 --> 00:23:47.440 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing?

00:23:50.480 --> 00:23:52.540 line:80%
Whether he's an heir apparent or not,

00:23:52.910 --> 00:23:54.350 line:80%
I'll flay him alive right now!

00:23:54.350 --> 00:23:55.960 line:80%
-Tell me where he is!
-Of course we'll flay him alive!

00:23:55.960 --> 00:23:57.000 line:80%
But not now!

00:23:58.000 --> 00:23:59.520 line:80%
We have another mission—

00:24:01.000 --> 00:24:03.330 line:80%
to bring the survivors of Lin'an back home

00:24:03.870 --> 00:24:05.070 line:80%
so they can live well.

00:24:15.960 --> 00:24:16.800 line:80%
But...

00:24:17.350 --> 00:24:18.800 line:80%
Lin'an is destroyed.

00:24:19.680 --> 00:24:20.940 line:80%
Where can we return to?

00:24:22.800 --> 00:24:24.390 line:80%
My father's dying wish

00:24:24.910 --> 00:24:27.110 line:80%
was for me to take good care of my mother.

00:24:27.240 --> 00:24:28.760 line:80%
Now that my mother is gone,

00:24:29.590 --> 00:24:31.320 line:80%
where... where can I go back to?

00:24:40.390 --> 00:24:41.790 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao is still alive.

00:24:42.680 --> 00:24:43.800 line:80%
And the rest of

00:24:44.150 --> 00:24:46.390 line:80%
the people of Lin'an are also alive.

00:24:48.630 --> 00:24:49.910 line:80%
As long as we are alive,

00:24:50.550 --> 00:24:52.070 line:80%
Lin'an is still alive.

00:24:53.800 --> 00:24:55.040 line:80%
Don't lose hope.

00:24:58.760 --> 00:25:00.280 line:80%
Remember this.

00:25:02.040 --> 00:25:03.760 line:80%
Let's take our revenge first,

00:25:05.200 --> 00:25:06.460 line:80%
then return to Lin'an.

00:25:07.280 --> 00:25:07.870 line:80%
Yes.

00:25:07.870 --> 00:25:08.550 line:80%
Right!

00:25:09.870 --> 00:25:12.630 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an has led troops
to destroy Qingfeng Stronghold,

00:25:12.630 --> 00:25:15.560 line:80%
so justice can be considered served
for Lin'an Town.

00:25:15.680 --> 00:25:16.760 line:80%
I swore an oath

00:25:18.240 --> 00:25:19.390 line:80%
to bring Changning

00:25:19.830 --> 00:25:20.720 line:80%
and all of you

00:25:20.720 --> 00:25:22.040 line:80%
back safely—

00:25:22.240 --> 00:25:23.440 line:80%
not a single one left.

00:25:26.680 --> 00:25:27.720 line:80%
As for revenge,

00:25:28.280 --> 00:25:29.740 line:80%
we need to plan carefully.

00:25:31.800 --> 00:25:32.680 line:80%
Understood.

00:25:42.070 --> 00:25:43.630 line:80%
Fellow folks of Lin'an,

00:25:45.240 --> 00:25:46.350 line:80%
rest in peace.

00:25:47.240 --> 00:25:47.910 line:80%
Mother,

00:25:49.000 --> 00:25:50.070 line:80%
rest in peace.

00:25:51.550 --> 00:25:52.590 line:80%
Rest in peace.

00:26:48.240 --> 00:26:49.170 line:80%
Don't be afraid.

00:26:49.310 --> 00:26:50.630 line:80%
It's me.

00:26:52.830 --> 00:26:55.150 line:80%
Sir, why are you here?

00:26:55.440 --> 00:26:58.680 line:80%
I found a quiet spot upstairs

00:26:58.680 --> 00:27:00.550 line:80%
to do some reading.

00:27:01.280 --> 00:27:04.200 line:80%
I didn't expect to find you here.

00:27:07.390 --> 00:27:08.760 line:80%
Did we disturb you?

00:27:10.240 --> 00:27:11.440 line:80%
No.

00:27:12.350 --> 00:27:14.630 line:80%
You were sleeping soundly just now.

00:27:14.910 --> 00:27:17.830 line:80%
Your sister is still missing,

00:27:17.830 --> 00:27:19.490 line:80%
your village was burned down,

00:27:19.550 --> 00:27:21.550 line:80%
and you are trapped here,

00:27:21.960 --> 00:27:24.440 line:80%
yet you can still sleep so soundly.

00:27:25.720 --> 00:27:29.590 line:80%
You really are a naive and fearless girl.

00:27:30.720 --> 00:27:32.800 line:80%
My parents told me when they were alive

00:27:32.800 --> 00:27:33.680 line:80%
that even if the sky falls,

00:27:33.680 --> 00:27:36.140 line:80%
there's always someone taller
to hold it up.

00:27:36.150 --> 00:27:38.000 line:80%
No matter what happens,

00:27:38.310 --> 00:27:39.590 line:80%
we should eat well,

00:27:39.720 --> 00:27:40.910 line:80%
sleep well,

00:27:41.150 --> 00:27:42.800 line:80%
and live well in the moment.

00:27:43.000 --> 00:27:45.530 line:80%
Focus on oneself
and ignore worldly affairs?

00:27:46.960 --> 00:27:49.520 line:80%
Your parents lacked education,

00:27:51.440 --> 00:27:53.300 line:80%
but they possessed great wisdom.

00:27:54.240 --> 00:27:56.280 line:80%
Do those brats

00:27:56.760 --> 00:27:58.630 line:80%
get along with you?

00:28:00.280 --> 00:28:02.830 line:80%
He started out bullying my family,

00:28:04.000 --> 00:28:06.000 line:80%
but I beat some sense into him.

00:28:06.590 --> 00:28:07.830 line:80%
Now,

00:28:08.550 --> 00:28:09.870 line:80%
we're like family.

00:28:10.070 --> 00:28:11.720 line:80%
Beat some sense into him?

00:28:12.830 --> 00:28:15.760 line:80%
You really are just like
my bratty disciple.

00:28:16.030 --> 00:28:18.760 line:80%
Stubborn and proud.

00:28:20.720 --> 00:28:22.960 line:80%
If you didn't have a husband,

00:28:22.960 --> 00:28:25.310 line:80%
you two could give it a try.

00:28:25.590 --> 00:28:26.240 line:80%
Old man,

00:28:26.240 --> 00:28:28.040 line:80%
don't play matchmaker blindly.

00:28:28.830 --> 00:28:30.240 line:80%
My Yan Zheng

00:28:30.590 --> 00:28:32.680 line:80%
is both capable and smart.

00:28:34.390 --> 00:28:36.650 line:80%
Although he pulls a long face sometimes,

00:28:37.240 --> 00:28:38.590 line:80%
I just like him.

00:28:40.870 --> 00:28:42.830 line:80%
My disciple isn't bad either.

00:28:43.280 --> 00:28:45.240 line:80%
He is well-versed
in both civil and military affairs,

00:28:45.240 --> 00:28:47.110 line:80%
and values friendship and loyalty.

00:28:47.110 --> 00:28:49.150 line:80%
He was hostile in his youth,

00:28:49.390 --> 00:28:51.520 line:80%
so I gave him the courtesy name Jiuheng,

00:28:51.520 --> 00:28:52.630 line:80%
just to temper him,

00:28:52.630 --> 00:28:55.520 line:80%
reminding him to think 9 times
before acting.

00:28:56.200 --> 00:28:59.150 line:80%
He hasn't let me down
these past few years.

00:28:59.520 --> 00:29:01.760 line:80%
Although he made his name at a young age,

00:29:01.760 --> 00:29:05.110 line:80%
he is as composed
as an experienced general.

00:29:05.280 --> 00:29:06.550 line:80%
Most importantly,

00:29:06.830 --> 00:29:08.680 line:80%
he is handsome

00:29:08.910 --> 00:29:10.800 line:80%
and has a flawless appearance.

00:29:11.830 --> 00:29:13.200 line:80%
If we're comparing looks,

00:29:13.200 --> 00:29:15.310 line:80%
my Yan Zheng is the best in the world.

00:29:19.480 --> 00:29:20.610 line:80%
Why do I keep feeling

00:29:20.830 --> 00:29:23.290 line:80%
that they are talking about
the same person?

00:29:25.000 --> 00:29:27.060 line:80%
I mean Changyu's matrilocal husband

00:29:29.680 --> 00:29:30.960 line:80%
Changyu's matrilocal husband

00:29:30.960 --> 00:29:33.200 line:80%
and that Old Tao's disciple.

00:29:36.440 --> 00:29:37.480 line:80%
This is none of your business.

00:29:37.480 --> 00:29:38.520 line:80%
Just go to sleep.

00:29:38.830 --> 00:29:39.550 line:80%
Go to sleep.

00:29:39.680 --> 00:29:41.590 line:80%
So he's a matrilocal husband?

00:29:45.910 --> 00:29:48.240 line:80%
What a pity for my disciple.

00:29:49.440 --> 00:29:53.110 line:80%
Let him remain a bachelor for now.

00:29:56.390 --> 00:29:57.480 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:30:08.800 --> 00:30:10.280 line:80%
When you sneeze,

00:30:10.520 --> 00:30:12.550 line:80%
it means someone is thinking of you.

00:30:13.440 --> 00:30:16.390 line:80%
I wonder which young lady

00:30:16.630 --> 00:30:18.480 line:80%
is missing you this time.

00:30:19.070 --> 00:30:20.910 line:80%
You're too noisy. Go away.

00:30:29.150 --> 00:30:31.750 line:80%
Who was the first to see the moon
over the river?

00:30:33.280 --> 00:30:35.410 line:80%
When did the first light of the moon...

00:30:36.350 --> 00:30:37.480 line:80%
fall on humanity?

00:31:03.960 --> 00:31:04.960 line:80%
My Lady.

00:31:07.680 --> 00:31:09.150 line:80%
I am no lady.

00:31:10.480 --> 00:31:12.880 line:80%
I'm just a maid
who was sent to his bed by you.

00:31:14.390 --> 00:31:16.030 line:80%
Although I used you,

00:31:16.350 --> 00:31:18.280 line:80%
I bear you no ill will.

00:31:18.520 --> 00:31:20.910 line:80%
You don't need to treat me as an enemy.

00:31:22.150 --> 00:31:24.040 line:80%
We can cooperate.

00:31:26.240 --> 00:31:27.040 line:80%
Get out.

00:31:27.480 --> 00:31:30.280 line:80%
Miss Yu,
you'd better consider yourself the lady.

00:31:30.630 --> 00:31:33.960 line:80%
Only then
will the Little Young Master survive

00:31:34.150 --> 00:31:35.440 line:80%
and have a future.

00:31:40.350 --> 00:31:41.310 line:80%
Bring him in.

00:31:43.440 --> 00:31:44.070 line:80%
Mother.

00:31:44.760 --> 00:31:45.520 line:80%
Bao'er?

00:31:45.960 --> 00:31:46.590 line:80%
Mother!

00:31:46.870 --> 00:31:48.070 line:80%
Fairy Sister.

00:31:50.960 --> 00:31:51.630 line:80%
Changning.

00:32:03.720 --> 00:32:04.980 line:80%
Why are you helping me?

00:32:06.720 --> 00:32:08.000 line:80%
What do you want?

00:32:08.800 --> 00:32:10.800 line:80%
Helping you is helping Great Yin.

00:32:12.040 --> 00:32:14.240 line:80%
I will keep the Little Young Master safe

00:32:14.720 --> 00:32:16.980 line:80%
and preserve the bloodline of Great Yin.

00:32:21.680 --> 00:32:23.680 line:80%
I hope the Young Master
and Little Young Master

00:32:23.680 --> 00:32:25.210 line:80%
will both be safe and sound.

00:32:34.240 --> 00:32:35.390 line:80%
Where are you?

00:32:36.520 --> 00:32:37.150 line:80%
In front of you.

00:32:37.150 --> 00:32:38.110 line:80%
Here.

00:32:38.550 --> 00:32:39.390 line:80%
Behind you.

00:32:39.390 --> 00:32:39.760 line:80%
Here?

00:32:39.760 --> 00:32:41.220 line:80%
-Behind you.
-Behind you.

00:32:41.630 --> 00:32:42.520 line:80%
I'm here!

00:32:42.830 --> 00:32:44.040 line:80%
-Behind you.
-Here!

00:32:44.310 --> 00:32:44.870 line:80%
Where?

00:32:45.280 --> 00:32:45.630 line:80%
Here?

00:32:45.630 --> 00:32:47.070 line:80%
On your right.

00:32:52.720 --> 00:32:53.390 line:80%
Here!

00:32:53.390 --> 00:32:54.440 line:80%
I'm here!

00:32:54.680 --> 00:32:55.390 line:80%
Where are you?

00:32:55.390 --> 00:32:56.310 line:80%
Behind you!

00:32:56.310 --> 00:32:57.070 line:80%
Watch out.

00:32:57.280 --> 00:32:58.280 line:80%
No, no, no.

00:32:59.630 --> 00:33:00.830 line:80%
Where are you?

00:33:01.870 --> 00:33:03.110 line:80%
I'm here!

00:33:04.200 --> 00:33:05.070 line:80%
Over here!

00:33:05.350 --> 00:33:05.910 line:80%
Here!

00:33:06.440 --> 00:33:07.000 line:80%
Here!

00:33:07.000 --> 00:33:08.110 line:80%
I'm here!

00:33:08.960 --> 00:33:10.620 line:80%
You are really good at hiding.

00:33:10.800 --> 00:33:11.760 line:80%
Where are you?

00:33:12.150 --> 00:33:12.870 line:80%
Here!

00:33:12.870 --> 00:33:15.070 line:80%
-Be careful, Your Lady.
-Where are you?

00:33:15.390 --> 00:33:16.800 line:80%
Is this what you call

00:33:17.040 --> 00:33:18.070 line:80%
a family reunion?

00:33:19.680 --> 00:33:20.480 line:80%
Look.

00:33:21.440 --> 00:33:22.870 line:80%
They are so happy now.

00:33:23.520 --> 00:33:24.200 line:80%
Here!

00:33:24.200 --> 00:33:26.480 line:80%
I heard your footsteps.

00:33:28.760 --> 00:33:30.000 line:80%
I'm here!

00:33:30.550 --> 00:33:31.480 line:80%
Someday,

00:33:31.830 --> 00:33:33.040 line:80%
I will be like you,

00:33:33.390 --> 00:33:35.630 line:80%
with a beloved woman and child

00:33:36.800 --> 00:33:37.960 line:80%
always by my side.

00:33:41.960 --> 00:33:43.200 line:80%
That day will come.

00:33:44.390 --> 00:33:45.040 line:80%
Got you!

00:33:45.040 --> 00:33:46.440 line:80%
-Mother!
-Fairy Sister!

00:33:50.000 --> 00:33:51.070 line:80%
Later,

00:33:51.070 --> 00:33:53.130 line:80%
let's play a game of deception, okay?

00:33:53.720 --> 00:33:56.050 line:80%
This game is called "Never Want to Leave."

00:33:56.200 --> 00:33:58.040 line:80%
We'll eat, drink, and play well,

00:33:58.040 --> 00:33:59.630 line:80%
and laugh as happily as we can,

00:33:59.630 --> 00:34:02.310 line:80%
making them believe
we'll never run away again.

00:34:03.070 --> 00:34:04.680 line:80%
When they let their guard down,

00:34:04.680 --> 00:34:05.760 line:80%
I'll take you away.

00:34:05.910 --> 00:34:06.680 line:80%
Got it?

00:34:10.600 --> 00:34:12.400 line:80%
Come on, let's go play this game.

00:34:15.870 --> 00:34:16.470 line:80%
Come on.

00:34:16.470 --> 00:34:17.310 line:80%
Say hello.

00:34:18.510 --> 00:34:19.680 line:80%
Have a big smile.

00:34:20.030 --> 00:34:23.229 line:80%
The happier you smile,
the sooner you can see your sister.

00:35:05.950 --> 00:35:07.470 line:80%
I haven't felt like this

00:35:07.830 --> 00:35:09.760 line:80%
in a very long time.

00:35:27.760 --> 00:35:29.090 line:80%
You're acting it wrong.

00:35:29.680 --> 00:35:31.080 line:80%
Next,

00:35:32.640 --> 00:35:34.560 line:80%
you should throw this jade pendant

00:35:34.560 --> 00:35:35.990 line:80%
at my face

00:35:36.560 --> 00:35:37.800 line:80%
and say it's a reward.

00:35:42.510 --> 00:35:43.680 line:80%
It's been 7 years.

00:35:53.200 --> 00:35:54.910 line:80%
Have you been with other men?

00:35:56.560 --> 00:35:57.760 line:80%
Only you.

00:35:59.120 --> 00:36:00.160 line:80%
Liar.

00:36:12.830 --> 00:36:14.120 line:80%
Help!

00:36:15.800 --> 00:36:17.200 line:80%
Fire!

00:36:17.310 --> 00:36:18.720 line:80%
Fire!

00:36:23.310 --> 00:36:24.870 line:80%
Help!

00:36:25.430 --> 00:36:27.080 line:80%
Help!

00:36:54.390 --> 00:36:54.950 line:80%
Hey!

00:36:54.950 --> 00:36:56.720 line:80%
Wake up! Wake up!

00:36:57.030 --> 00:36:59.640 line:80%
Why do I get into such trouble
as soon as I arrive?

00:36:59.640 --> 00:37:01.200 line:80%
Don't die here!

00:37:30.720 --> 00:37:31.920 line:80%
Luckily, you woke up.

00:37:32.470 --> 00:37:34.200 line:80%
I guess I did a good deed.

00:37:34.640 --> 00:37:37.440 line:80%
I hope Bodhisattva blesses me
to return home soon.

00:37:45.640 --> 00:37:46.680 line:80%
And you.

00:37:46.910 --> 00:37:48.170 line:80%
Since you're not dead,

00:37:48.240 --> 00:37:49.770 line:80%
live a good life from now on.

00:37:51.030 --> 00:37:51.870 line:80%
I'm leaving.

00:38:06.280 --> 00:38:07.310 line:80%
It's you?

00:38:16.800 --> 00:38:18.030 line:80%
It's a reward.

00:38:28.030 --> 00:38:29.120 line:80%
All these years,

00:38:30.390 --> 00:38:32.160 line:80%
have you ever thought of me

00:38:33.120 --> 00:38:34.580 line:80%
in the middle of the night?

00:38:36.950 --> 00:38:37.720 line:80%
Yes.

00:38:39.120 --> 00:38:40.160 line:80%
In my nightmares.

00:38:43.470 --> 00:38:45.080 line:80%
Better than never.

00:39:17.200 --> 00:39:18.640 line:80%
The Heir Apparent has ordered

00:39:18.640 --> 00:39:19.970 line:80%
to take this woman away.

00:39:20.560 --> 00:39:21.800 line:80%
Anyone who disobeys

00:39:22.310 --> 00:39:23.350 line:80%
will be beheaded.

00:39:23.910 --> 00:39:25.120 line:80%
No one can take her

00:39:25.640 --> 00:39:26.870 line:80%
without the Young Master's order.

00:39:26.870 --> 00:39:27.600 line:80%
How dare you!

00:39:28.720 --> 00:39:29.430 line:80%
Try me.

00:39:31.390 --> 00:39:32.320 line:80%
What's going on?

00:39:41.910 --> 00:39:43.240 line:80%
Who started it?

00:39:44.680 --> 00:39:46.240 line:80%
They were going to hurt
the Little Young Master.

00:39:46.240 --> 00:39:47.800 line:80%
I had no choice but to act.

00:39:48.120 --> 00:39:49.720 line:80%
Otherwise, Her Ladyship...

00:39:50.160 --> 00:39:50.960 line:80%
Her Ladyship?

00:39:51.200 --> 00:39:52.640 line:80%
She's nothing!

00:39:53.160 --> 00:39:54.600 line:80%
We can't let a woman

00:39:54.760 --> 00:39:56.360 line:80%
ruin Yuanqing's grand plan.

00:39:57.280 --> 00:39:58.510 line:80%
Yuanqing is on the front line,

00:39:58.510 --> 00:40:00.160 line:80%
risking his life to defend us.

00:40:00.160 --> 00:40:02.080 line:80%
Even if he wants to sacrifice my son
as an offering,

00:40:02.080 --> 00:40:03.080 line:80%
I won't say a word.

00:40:03.350 --> 00:40:04.310 line:80%
You can't

00:40:04.310 --> 00:40:05.510 line:80%
separate personal and official matters.

00:40:05.510 --> 00:40:08.240 line:80%
You should be punished
according to martial law!

00:40:09.280 --> 00:40:09.910 line:80%
Min!

00:40:10.430 --> 00:40:11.080 line:80%
Min!

00:40:11.800 --> 00:40:13.060 line:80%
Please don't be angry.

00:40:13.160 --> 00:40:14.560 line:80%
It's bad for your health.

00:40:14.600 --> 00:40:15.240 line:80%
Yuanqing,

00:40:15.680 --> 00:40:16.610 line:80%
why are you here?

00:40:18.200 --> 00:40:19.280 line:80%
It's all because my men

00:40:19.280 --> 00:40:20.210 line:80%
were incapable.

00:40:20.760 --> 00:40:21.600 line:80%
Guards!

00:40:21.600 --> 00:40:23.080 line:80%
Drag them out and behead them!

00:40:23.080 --> 00:40:23.560 line:80%
Yes!

00:40:23.560 --> 00:40:24.030 line:80%
Wait!

00:40:25.510 --> 00:40:25.990 line:80%
Min,

00:40:26.720 --> 00:40:27.720 line:80%
we're brothers.

00:40:27.990 --> 00:40:29.390 line:80%
There's no need for this.

00:40:31.280 --> 00:40:32.080 line:80%
You may leave.

00:40:32.310 --> 00:40:33.120 line:80%
Yes!

00:40:35.560 --> 00:40:36.830 line:80%
Take that little girl away.

00:40:36.830 --> 00:40:37.160 line:80%
Yes!

00:40:37.200 --> 00:40:38.200 line:80%
Stay away!

00:40:38.470 --> 00:40:39.470 line:80%
Stay away!

00:40:39.760 --> 00:40:40.910 line:80%
Let go of Changning!

00:40:40.910 --> 00:40:42.280 line:80%
-Let go!
-Let's go!

00:40:47.120 --> 00:40:49.030 line:80%
Changning!

00:40:50.030 --> 00:40:51.310 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:40:54.990 --> 00:40:58.620 line:80%
[Lucheng Army Camp]

00:41:10.560 --> 00:41:12.120 line:80%
Since when
did the dignified Marquis of Wu'an

00:41:12.120 --> 00:41:13.280 line:80%
develop this childish habit

00:41:13.280 --> 00:41:15.350 line:80%
of eating snacks and sweets?

00:41:15.430 --> 00:41:16.690 line:80%
None of your business.

00:41:16.950 --> 00:41:18.480 line:80%
At least you don't have any.

00:41:18.830 --> 00:41:19.720 line:80%
I don't?

00:41:21.200 --> 00:41:22.470 line:80%
If I wanted candy,

00:41:22.470 --> 00:41:23.910 line:80%
countless noble ladies

00:41:23.910 --> 00:41:25.570 line:80%
would bring a candy shop to me.

00:41:27.240 --> 00:41:30.770 line:80%
Your Lordship, there's a letter
from the Chongzhou Army scout.

00:41:39.120 --> 00:41:40.350 line:80%
This Sui Yuanqing

00:41:40.800 --> 00:41:43.390 line:80%
wants me to trade Yanzhou for Changning.

00:41:47.600 --> 00:41:48.800 line:80%
This Sui Yuanqing

00:41:49.160 --> 00:41:51.090 line:80%
is getting more and more arrogant.

00:41:54.030 --> 00:41:55.080 line:80%
Pass on my order.

00:41:55.760 --> 00:41:58.310 line:80%
Have the vanguard battalion
follow me to Baxia

00:41:58.310 --> 00:41:59.710 line:80%
to bring my daughter back

00:41:59.990 --> 00:42:01.560 line:80%
without a scratch.

00:42:01.720 --> 00:42:02.390 line:80%
Yes!